Christine Rayner https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Christine_Rayner 0 Christine Rayner was a British actress of the silent era.She was born 21 October 1888 in Holborn, London and died in Exmouth, Devon on 26 September 1973 in Exmouth, Devon at age 84.
